00:09:53,259 --> 00:09:54,827
♪ LOVE YOU MOST OF ALL

217
00:09:54,860 --> 00:09:55,828
♪ ONCE MORE

218
00:09:55,861 --> 00:10:01,233
♪ I HAVE A FAMILY

219
00:10:08,975 --> 00:10:11,143
Miss Clavel:
DOUX REVES, MES CHERIES.

220
00:10:11,177 --> 00:10:12,178
SWEET DREAMS.

221
00:10:12,211 --> 00:10:15,348
TOMORROW WILL BE
AN EXCITING DAY!

222
00:10:15,381 --> 00:10:16,983
SLEEP WELL.

223
00:10:17,016 --> 00:10:18,918
All: GOOD NIGHT, GOOD NIGHT,

224
00:10:18,951 --> 00:10:21,253
DEAR MISS CLAVEL.

225
00:10:25,458 --> 00:10:27,793
Chloe: PSST! MADELINE!

226
00:10:27,827 --> 00:10:28,894
ARE YOU AWAKE?

227
00:10:28,928 --> 00:10:29,628
OF COURSE!

228
00:10:29,662 --> 00:10:31,931
THIS IS NO TIME
FOR ME TO SLEEP.

229
00:10:31,964 --> 00:10:33,332
NOR ME!

230
00:10:33,366 --> 00:10:34,066
OR ME!

231
00:10:34,100 --> 00:10:36,068
DO YOU THINK
HE'LL HAVE RED HAIR?

232
00:10:36,102 --> 00:10:36,836
LIKE MINE?

233
00:10:36,869 --> 00:10:40,006
WHO WILL HE BE,
THIS UNCLE HORST?

234
00:10:40,039 --> 00:10:40,840
I KNOW.

235
00:10:40,873 --> 00:10:42,475
A FAMOUS NOVELIST

236
00:10:42,508 --> 00:10:43,376
FROM THE ACADEMY,

237
00:10:43,409 --> 00:10:46,212
LIKE OUR BELOVED
VICTOR HUGO.

238
00:10:46,245 --> 00:10:48,014
A BRAVE SOLDIER.

239
00:10:48,047 --> 00:10:49,448
NON, NON.

240
00:10:49,482 --> 00:10:50,116
A GENERAL

241
00:10:50,149 --> 00:10:53,486
WITH MEDALS
AND DECORATIONS.

242
00:10:53,519 --> 00:10:54,487
OR...

243
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:55,154
AN ADMIRAL

244
00:10:55,187 --> 00:10:57,823
IN COMMAND
OF HIS OWN FLEET.

245
00:10:57,857 --> 00:10:59,125
NON,
 NON!

246
00:10:59,158 --> 00:11:00,926
HE MUST BE A PRINCE

247
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:03,929
WITH A CASTLE
AND FINE HORSES.

248
00:11:03,963 --> 00:11:04,797
MADELINE?

249
00:11:04,830 --> 00:11:06,198
WHAT DO
YOU
 SEE?

250
00:11:06,232 --> 00:11:09,935
HE'S SURE
TO BE HANDSOME...

251
00:11:11,504 --> 00:11:14,040
AND INTELLIGENT...

252
00:11:15,141 --> 00:11:17,209
AND RICH...

253
00:11:18,444 --> 00:11:20,246
AND SLENDER...

254
00:11:20,279 --> 00:11:22,782
AND VERY, VERY KIND.

255
00:11:22,815 --> 00:11:25,284
MONSIEUR PERFECT.

256
00:11:26,285 --> 00:11:27,019
Narrator: IN THE MORNING

257
00:11:27,053 --> 00:11:29,422
AS THEY LEFT
THE OLD HOUSE BEHIND,

258
00:11:29,455 --> 00:11:31,190
THERE WAS ONLY ONE SUBJECT

259
00:11:31,223 --> 00:11:32,958
ON MADELINE'S MIND.

260
00:11:32,992 --> 00:11:35,127
BUON GIORNO!

261
00:11:35,161 --> 00:11:36,128
DID YOU KNOW?

262
00:11:36,162 --> 00:11:38,030
MY UNCLE IS COMING!

263
00:11:38,064 --> 00:11:39,331
SÌ?

264
00:11:39,365 --> 00:11:40,800
FROM VIENNA.

265
00:11:40,833 --> 00:11:41,567
AH! HA HA HA!

266
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:44,437
THEN HERE IS A WALTZ
IN HIS HONOR.

267
00:11:44,470 --> 00:11:45,871
[HURDY-GURDY
PLAYS WALTZ]

268
00:11:45,905 --> 00:11:48,407
[GIRLS LAUGH]

269
00:11:56,182 --> 00:11:57,216
DID YOU KNOW?

270
00:11:57,249 --> 00:11:59,351
TODAY I HAVE
A VISITOR.

271
00:11:59,385 --> 00:12:01,854
WHO CAN THAT BE?

272
00:12:01,887 --> 00:12:04,090
[WHISPERS] It's
my uncle from Vienna.

273
00:12:04,123 --> 00:12:05,958
FOR YOUR UNCLE.

274
00:12:05,991 --> 00:12:06,959
MERCI.

275
00:12:06,992 --> 00:12:09,995
Miss Clavel: MADELINE!

276
00:12:10,896 --> 00:12:12,898
GUESS WHO THOSE ARE FOR!

277
00:12:12,932 --> 00:12:15,201
YOUR UNCLE, MADELINE?

278
00:12:15,234 --> 00:12:17,536
[GASPS] WHO TOLD YOU?

279
00:12:17,570 --> 00:12:19,538
HEE HEE HEE!

280
00:12:19,572 --> 00:12:22,041
[ALL LAUGH]
NOW EVERYBODY KNOWS!

281
00:12:22,074 --> 00:12:25,444
Narrator: POOR MADELINE
COULD DO NOTHING BUT WAIT.

282
00:12:25,478 --> 00:12:29,215
FINALLY, A TAXI
PULLED UP AT THE GATE.

283
00:12:29,248 --> 00:12:30,382
HE'S HERE!

284
00:12:30,416 --> 00:12:31,517
HA HA HA!

285
00:12:31,550 --> 00:12:32,518
ALORS!
 WAIT!

286
00:12:32,551 --> 00:12:36,388
WE MUST MAKE A GOOD
FIRST IMPRESSION,
NON?

287
00:12:36,422 --> 00:12:38,090
OUI!

288
00:12:38,124 --> 00:12:40,993
All: HA HA HA!

289
00:12:41,026 --> 00:12:43,963
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

290
00:12:46,599 --> 00:12:47,500
FRAULEIN CLAVEL,
I PRESUME.

291
00:12:47,533 --> 00:12:50,836
JA,
 I AM MADELINE'S
 UNCLE HORST.

292
00:12:50,870 --> 00:12:52,438
MAIS OUI, MONSIEUR.

293
00:12:52,471 --> 00:12:55,574
AND THIS IS MADELINE!

294
00:12:55,608 --> 00:12:57,009
BONJOUR, MONSIEUR.

295
00:12:57,042 --> 00:13:00,045
AH, HOW COULD I NOT
RECOGNIZE MY OWN KIND?

296
00:13:00,079 --> 00:13:01,614
AND EVERY BIT
AS BEAUTIFUL

297
00:13:01,647 --> 00:13:03,048
AS YOUR
MUTTER.

298
00:13:03,082 --> 00:13:03,949
MAMA?!

299
00:13:03,983 --> 00:13:05,251
YOU KNEW HER?!

300
00:13:05,284 --> 00:13:06,886
HA HA HA! BUT OF COURSE.

301
00:13:06,919 --> 00:13:08,888
I AM YOUR UNCLE,NEIN?

302
00:13:08,921 --> 00:13:09,889
FAMILY!

303
00:13:09,922 --> 00:13:10,956
FAMILY?

304
00:13:10,990 --> 00:13:13,392
I DID NOT KNOW
I HAD ANY.

305
00:13:13,425 --> 00:13:14,493
IST GUT, JA?

306
00:13:14,527 --> 00:13:15,628
OH,
 OUI!

307
00:13:15,661 --> 00:13:17,129
JA!

308
00:13:17,163 --> 00:13:18,597
All:
JA!

309
00:13:18,631 --> 00:13:19,899
AND NOW...

310
00:13:19,932 --> 00:13:21,901
THE GIFTS!

311
00:13:22,334 --> 00:13:25,037
Girls: OOH!

312
00:13:25,070 --> 00:13:27,039
AHH!

313
00:13:27,072 --> 00:13:30,309
Girls: WHAT CAN IT BE? HE
BROUGHT GIFTS FOR ALL OF US!

314
00:13:30,342 --> 00:13:32,344
Narrator: THERE WERE
RIBBONS AND BOXES

315
00:13:32,378 --> 00:13:33,212
ALL OVER THE PLACE

316
00:13:33,245 --> 00:13:35,948
AS EACH GIRL UNCOVERED
A COLLAR OF LACE.

317
00:13:35,981 --> 00:13:38,050
SO BEAUTIFUL!

318
00:13:38,083 --> 00:13:39,084
AND FROM MY UNCLE!

319
00:13:39,118 --> 00:13:42,955
All: MERCI
BEAUCOUP,
MONSIEUR HORST!

320
00:13:42,988 --> 00:13:45,958
YOU ARE MOST KIND,
HERR HORST.

321
00:13:45,991 --> 00:13:47,226
NO, NO, NO.
IT IS MY PLEASURE.

322
00:13:47,259 --> 00:13:51,297
IT IS GOOD ETIQUETTE, 
JA,
 TO BRING
 PARTING GIFTS.

323
00:13:51,330 --> 00:13:52,398
Both: PARTING?!

324
00:13:52,431 --> 00:13:54,233
I DO NOT
UNDERSTAND.

325
00:13:54,266 --> 00:13:57,536
PERHAPS I SHOULD START
AT THE BEGINNING.

326
00:13:57,570 --> 00:14:01,106
AS YOU CAN SEE,
THE COURTS HAVE MADE ME
MADELINE'S NEW GUARDIAN.

327
00:14:01,140 --> 00:14:04,076
AFTER ALL, THAT IS
HOW IT SHOULD BE,JA?

328
00:14:04,109 --> 00:14:05,177
WE ARE FAMILY.

329
00:14:05,211 --> 00:14:06,445
FAMILY!

330
00:14:06,478 --> 00:14:08,314
BUT...
Girls: BUT?

331
00:14:08,347 --> 00:14:10,082
I LIVE IN VIENNA,

332
00:14:10,115 --> 00:14:11,450
AND MY WORK
IS IN VIENNA.

333
00:14:11,483 --> 00:14:13,452
AND THERE IS
 A VERY, VERY FINE,

334
00:14:13,485 --> 00:14:15,654
EXCLUSIVE
FINISHING SCHOOL...

335
00:14:15,688 --> 00:14:18,224
All: [GASPS] IN VIENNA?!

336
00:14:18,257 --> 00:14:19,491
JA.
 EXACTLY.

337
00:14:19,525 --> 00:14:21,193
I KNEW YOU WOULD
UNDERSTAND.

338
00:14:21,227 --> 00:14:22,995
LEAVE MY FRIENDS?

339
00:14:23,028 --> 00:14:24,096
LEAVE PARIS?

340
00:14:24,129 --> 00:14:27,466
FOR THE FINE VIENNESE
FINISHING SCHOOL.

341
00:14:27,499 --> 00:14:28,667
OOH, LA LA!

342
00:14:28,701 --> 00:14:31,070
MADELINE IS
TO BE FINISHED?!

343
00:14:31,103 --> 00:14:34,373
YOU WILL BE EDUCATED
MIT
 ROYALTY!

344
00:14:34,406 --> 00:14:35,474
ROYALTY?

345
00:14:35,507 --> 00:14:37,443
OH, IT IS THE VERY BEST
OF SCHOOLS.

346
00:14:37,476 --> 00:14:40,946
I BELIEVE YOUR MOTHER
MAY HAVE ATTENDED
AT ONE POINT.

347
00:14:40,980 --> 00:14:43,115
THE SAME SCHOOL AS MAMA!

348
00:14:43,148 --> 00:14:44,984
IT MUST BE WONDERFUL!

349
00:14:45,017 --> 00:14:47,987
TOMORROW, WE TAKE
THE ORIENT EXPRESS.

350
00:14:48,020 --> 00:14:48,654
TOMORROW?!

351
00:14:48,687 --> 00:14:51,423
Girls:
ORIENT EXPRESS?!

352
00:14:51,457 --> 00:14:52,191
IT LEAVES FOR VIENNA

353
00:14:52,224 --> 00:14:54,994
AT PRECISELY 10:05
IN THE MORNING.

354
00:14:55,027 --> 00:14:56,262
I WILL BE HERE AT 9:00.

355
00:14:56,295 --> 00:14:58,564
PLEASE,
YOU WILL BE PACKED.JA.

356
00:14:58,597 --> 00:14:59,365
BUT...

357
00:14:59,398 --> 00:15:02,134
Girls, sadly: OHH!

358
00:15:03,035 --> 00:15:03,636
OH!

359
00:15:03,669 --> 00:15:04,670
EH, MONSIEUR.

360
00:15:04,703 --> 00:15:06,038
EH, WE HOPED
YOU WOULD DINE

361
00:15:06,071 --> 00:15:08,240
WITH US
THIS EVENING,
NON?

362
00:15:08,274 --> 00:15:10,676
MOST HONORED.

363
00:15:11,644 --> 00:15:13,012
MEIN
 LIEBCHEN,

364
00:15:13,045 --> 00:15:15,381
UNTIL THIS EVENING.

365
00:15:16,015 --> 00:15:18,584
AU REVOIR,
 UNCLE HORST!

366
00:15:21,053 --> 00:15:22,321
[WOOF WOOF]

367
00:15:22,354 --> 00:15:23,555
OH, GENEVIEVE.

368
00:15:23,589 --> 00:15:24,757
IT IS SO WONDERFUL

369
00:15:24,790 --> 00:15:26,191
TO HAVE AN UNCLE,

370
00:15:26,225 --> 00:15:28,727
BUT IT IS
NOT SO WONDERFUL

371
00:15:28,761 --> 00:15:29,595
TO LEAVE.

372
00:15:29,628 --> 00:15:32,731
YET IT MUST BE
 THE RIGHT THING TO DO.

373
00:15:32,765 --> 00:15:37,636
MY UNCLE WOULD ONLY WANT
THE VERY BEST FOR ME.

374
00:15:37,670 --> 00:15:39,204
NON?

375
00:15:39,238 --> 00:15:41,140
HEE HEE HEE!

376
00:15:41,173 --> 00:15:42,741
OUI!

377
00:15:45,644 --> 00:15:47,212
Narrator:
THEN SOMETHING OCCURRED

378
00:15:47,246 --> 00:15:49,381
OUT OF MADELINE'S VIEW.

379
00:15:49,415 --> 00:15:51,417
UNCLE HORST PAID THE CABBIE

380
00:15:51,450 --> 00:15:54,353
AND BADE HIM ADIEU,

381
00:15:54,386 --> 00:15:56,088
THEN STRUCK OFF ON FOOT

382
00:15:56,121 --> 00:15:58,691
DOWN THE LONG AVENUE.

383
00:15:58,724 --> 00:15:59,458
REMEMBER, GIRLS,

384
00:15:59,491 --> 00:16:02,728
WE MUST SHOW
MADELINE'S UNCLE HORST

385
00:16:02,761 --> 00:16:03,495
THAT WE ARE AS GOOD

386
00:16:03,529 --> 00:16:06,198
AS ANY VIENNESE
FINISHING SCHOOL.

387
00:16:06,231 --> 00:16:08,634
THEN PERHAPS HE WILL
LET HER STAY WITH US!

388
00:16:08,667 --> 00:16:12,538
WE WILL BE
TRÈS
 DELICATE,
NON?

389
00:16:12,571 --> 00:16:13,172
All:
OUI!

390
00:16:13,205 --> 00:16:14,606
TRÈS
 POLITE!

391
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:15,808
TRÈS
 ELEGANT!

392
00:16:15,841 --> 00:16:17,776
All:
TRÈS
 LADYLIKE!

393
00:16:17,810 --> 00:16:20,279
I WILL ASK PAPA
AND MAMA TO ATTEND.

394
00:16:20,312 --> 00:16:22,748
THEY, TOO, HAVE
DINED WITH ROYALTY.

395
00:16:22,781 --> 00:16:24,516
AH! PERFECT!

396
00:16:24,550 --> 00:16:26,285
AND I WILL INVITE
THE CHAIRMAN

397
00:16:26,318 --> 00:16:28,587
OF THE SCHOOL:
LORD CUCUFACE.

398
00:16:28,620 --> 00:16:31,590
WE WILL MAKE
A VERY GOOD IMPRESSION.

399
00:16:31,623 --> 00:16:34,526
All:
MAIS
 OUI!

400
00:16:37,696 --> 00:16:39,832
SEÑOR AMBASSADOR
OF SPAIN

401
00:16:39,865 --> 00:16:42,234
AND HIS WIFE.

402
00:16:42,267 --> 00:16:44,203
ES UN PLACER.

403
00:16:44,236 --> 00:16:45,170
LIKEWISE, I AM SURE.

404
00:16:45,204 --> 00:16:49,675
OH, AND I HAVE THE HONOR
TO REPRESENT THE KING.

405
00:16:49,708 --> 00:16:52,778
AND MADELINE PLAYS
WITH OUR SON PEPITO.

406
00:16:52,811 --> 00:16:55,714
I AM A PERSONAL FRIEND
OF MANY KINGS.

407
00:16:55,748 --> 00:16:57,149
AND AT THE SCHOOL
IN VIENNA,

408
00:16:57,182 --> 00:17:00,786
MADELINE WILL STUDY
WITH PRINCESSES.

409
00:17:02,855 --> 00:17:05,824
Miss Clavel:
LORD CUCUFACE.

410
00:17:05,858 --> 00:17:06,558
HERR HORST,

411
00:17:06,592 --> 00:17:09,561
I'M SURPRISED
WE HAVE NEVER MET.

412
00:17:09,595 --> 00:17:10,763
I HAVE MANY FRIENDS

413
00:17:10,796 --> 00:17:13,165
IN HIGH PLACES
IN VIENNA.

414
00:17:13,198 --> 00:17:14,166
JA?

415
00:17:14,199 --> 00:17:15,234
YES, INDEED.

416
00:17:15,267 --> 00:17:18,604
FOR EXAMPLE,
THERE'S BARON, UM--

417
00:17:18,637 --> 00:17:20,272
UH, COUNT, UH--

418
00:17:20,305 --> 00:17:20,939
[COUGHS]

419
00:17:20,973 --> 00:17:23,776
SO MANY
PERHAPS YOU FORGET.

420
00:17:23,809 --> 00:17:25,310
WELL, UH, Y-YES.

421
00:17:25,344 --> 00:17:26,078
QUITE--QUITE RIGHT.

422
00:17:26,111 --> 00:17:29,181
MESDAMES
ET MESSIEURS,

423
00:17:29,214 --> 00:17:31,650
DINNER IS SERVED.

424
00:17:32,785 --> 00:17:33,485
HERE AT SCHOOL,

425
00:17:33,519 --> 00:17:36,455
I HAVE LEARNED
TO PLAY THE PIANO.

426
00:17:36,488 --> 00:17:37,756
MOST BENEFICIAL,

427
00:17:37,790 --> 00:17:38,490
BUT IN VIENNA,

428
00:17:38,524 --> 00:17:40,859
YOU WILL LEARN
TO PLAY THE FLUTE.

429
00:17:40,893 --> 00:17:43,495
SHE HAS ALSO
LEARNED TO PAINT.

430
00:17:43,529 --> 00:17:45,497
IN VIENNA, YOU WILL
LEARN TO SCULPT.

431
00:17:45,531 --> 00:17:48,367
AND SHE'S
LEARNED, UM...

432
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:49,768
FOOTBALL!

433
00:17:49,802 --> 00:17:50,702
[GASPS]

434
00:17:50,736 --> 00:17:52,137
SHE MEANS...

435
00:17:52,171 --> 00:17:52,905
PHYSICS.

436
00:17:52,938 --> 00:17:54,773
[CHUCKLES] YOUNG
LADIES DO NOT NEED

437
00:17:54,807 --> 00:17:55,641
TO KNOW SUCH THINGS.

438
00:17:55,674 --> 00:17:58,744
OUR GIRLS ARE--ARE
QUITE TOP-OF-THE-LINE,

439
00:17:58,777 --> 00:17:59,578
ARE THEY NOT?

440
00:17:59,611 --> 00:18:01,747
NOT AS TOP
AS VIENNA.

441
00:18:01,780 --> 00:18:02,481
REALLY?

442
00:18:02,514 --> 00:18:06,351
I SAY, WE HAD
A GIRL YEARS AGO--

443
00:18:06,385 --> 00:18:08,187
MARRIED A DUKE.

444
00:18:08,220 --> 00:18:10,889
AND ONE WHO IS NOW
A FAMOUS WRITER.

445
00:18:10,923 --> 00:18:11,890
IN MADELINE'S NEW CLASS,

446
00:18:11,924 --> 00:18:15,727
THERE WILL BE 3 GIRLS
WHO ARE ALREADY DUCHESSES.

447
00:18:15,761 --> 00:18:16,895
4 CONTESSAS,

448
00:18:16,929 --> 00:18:18,530
2 PRINCESSES,

449
00:18:18,564 --> 00:18:21,467
AND AN EMPRESS TO BE!

450
00:18:21,500 --> 00:18:22,568
[GASPS]
Lord Cucuface: UM...

451
00:18:22,601 --> 00:18:26,472
I BELIEVE
THAT OUR GIRLS HAVE
SOMETHING VERY SPECIAL

452
00:18:26,505 --> 00:18:28,574
FOR US THIS EVENING.

453
00:18:36,748 --> 00:18:39,751
I COUNT
LIKE A COUNTESS.

454
00:18:39,785 --> 00:18:40,786
[PLAYING]

455
00:18:40,819 --> 00:18:43,856
I SPEAK DUTCH
LIKE A DUCHESS.

456
00:18:43,889 --> 00:18:44,556
[PLAYING]

457
00:18:44,590 --> 00:18:48,260
AND SHE PRINTS
LIKE A PRINCESS!

