484
00:19:46,952 --> 00:19:48,654
♪
TRÈS, TRES
 WELL-TRAVELED ♪

485
00:19:48,687 --> 00:19:52,324
♪ AND
TRÈS, TRES
 WELL-READ ♪

486
00:19:54,526 --> 00:19:56,695
♪ A FINE UPBRINGING
YOU'VE BEEN GIVEN ♪

487
00:19:56,728 --> 00:19:58,463
